Name:          toolbox
Version:       0.1.00.0

%global goipath github.com/akdev1l/%{name}
%gometa

Release:       8%{?dist}
Summary:       Tool for containerized command line environments on Linux

License:       ASL 2.0
URL:           https://github.com/akdev1l/%{name}
